{"tid":1115394,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【「食」得好密】上月一齊撐枱腳？黃心穎稱呼安仔「brothers」","createTime":"2019-04-19T06:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T17:46:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5db79d57fa8e50962e61e04b28d89adefdde89f","tid":1115394,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"許志安與黃心穎本來大攬都拉唔埋，年齡差距逾廿載，男的有「童話式嬌妻」Sammi，女的也有「筍盤男友」馬國明，所以過往即使心穎明目張膽在IG貼與安仔合照，大家都只會當平常事，不會覺得有問題。<br />\n但自從「安心偷食」事件不斷發酵，網民亦開始翻舊賬，《蘋果》日前已發現「安心」幾乎月月見（相關新聞： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xn8GCx），近日再有眼利網民發現「安心」在上月原來曾約會去九龍城一間菜館食晚飯，菜館亦有將二人當晚跟店員的合照放上網。但就未有提及當晚只有二人撐枱腳，還是有其他人同行。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xn8GCx%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%BC%E5%88%A9%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E3%80%8D%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%9B%BE%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%80%E9%96%93%E8%8F%9C%E9%A4%A8%E9%A3%9F%E6%99%9A%E9%A3%AF%EF%BC%8C%E8%8F%9C%E9%A4%A8%E4%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%B0%87%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%B6%E6%99%9A%E8%B7%9F%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7%E6%94%BE%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E3%80%82%E4%BD%86%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A%E7%95%B6%E6%99%9A%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%90%E6%9E%B1%E8%85%B3%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%82&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=b91790d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xn8GCx），近日再有眼利網民發現「安心」在上月原來曾約會去九龍城一間菜館食晚飯，菜館亦有將二人當晚跟店員的合照放上網。但就未有提及當晚只有二人撐枱腳，還是有其他人同行。</a><br />\n根據相片上載日期顯示，「安心」飯局發生在上月1日，當晚兩人雖然沒有一齊和店員合照，但就分別與店內職員影相，明顯有所避忌。當時菜館人員未發現「安心」關係，還在社交網開心留言：「嚟XX食飯，順便撞星星#許志安#心穎BB。」有人貼相後還在IG story貼文寫：「當時佢（許志安）係同蔡一智嚟㗎」。其實這間菜館向來吸引不少明星幫襯，如黃子華、林嘉欣、吳岱融、周家怡、陸永等等，所以「安心」當晚一齊去食飯，店內職員都好難察覺二人的曖昧關係。<br />\n另外，有指「安心」其實已暗交兩年，在安仔公司同事的IG上，亦發現心穎原來在2017年已成功埋堆，與安仔、阿Ken和男同事合照時更表情多多，伸晒脷，非常鬼馬，當時心穎還興奮留言：「hahhaha good times. brothers」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190418/large/1555570194_9d3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190418%2Flarge%2F1555570194_9d3b.jpg&h=e4eba697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安仔和心穎上月又一齊去九龍城一間明星飯堂疑似撐枱腳。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190419/59502805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190419%2F59502805&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=d58df4f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190419%2F59502805&h=fa1b44dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190419/59502805</a>"},{"pid":"a1953cd4fca80da2d4730fb969d6038caee448c3","tid":1115394,"uid":235546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"我稱呼黃心穎chicken"},{"pid":"8f134045793f9239640e6e086ec52b47ef7cfdc9","tid":1115394,"uid":188411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:03:58.000Z","msg":"即係屌屎忽？"},{"pid":"e9be466dae497755307aa0785ac9995de66dacc2","tid":1115394,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"契哥契上床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da81c8a907b68e7796293dca8a3e7ae92a04909e","tid":1115394,"uid":229270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:46:14.000Z","msg":"雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}